lead_paragraph: Unseeded Stefanie Voegele of Switzerland upset sixth-seeded Lesia Tsurenko of Ukraine 6-4, 6-0 on Monday to advance to the second round of the Katowice Open.

headline.print_headline: Voegele Upsets Tsurenko in 1st Round of Katowice Open
